  2→   ImageGallery — CSS Module
  3→   Gallery with hover zoom, thumbnails, lightbox
  4→   ============================================ */
  5→
  6→/* Gallery container */
  7→.gallery {
  8→  position: relative;
  9→  display: flex;
 10→  flex-direction: column;
 11→  gap: var(--spacing-3);
 12→}
 13→
 14→/* Badge overlay */
 15→.gallery-badge {
